        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>True Cost Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the President's annual budget submission to Congress to include estimates of the cost per individual taxpayer for (1) the public debt, and (2) any projected budget deficit for a fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
